function Splash({onDone}){const t=T();const [p,setP]=useState(0);useEffect(()=>{const ts=[setTimeout(()=>setP(1),280),setTimeout(()=>setP(2),950),setTimeout(()=>setP(3),1850),setTimeout(onDone,3050)];return()=>ts.forEach(clearTimeout);},[onDone]);return <div style={{position:"fixed",inset:0,background:t.bg,display:"flex",flexDirection:"column",alignItems:"center",justifyContent:"center",zIndex:999,overflow:"hidden"}}><div style={{position:"absolute",inset:0,background:`radial-gradient(ellipse at 30% 40%,${t.purple}1a 0%,transparent 55%),radial-gradient(ellipse at 70% 60%,${t.accent}10 0%,transparent 55%)`}}/>{[480,340,210].map((sz,i)=><div key={i} style={{position:"absolute",width:sz,height:sz,borderRadius:"50%",border:`1px solid ${i===0?t.purple+"18":t.accent+"12"}`,animation:`rRing 3.5s ease-out ${i*0.7}s infinite`}}/>)}<div style={{opacity:p>=1?1:0,transform:p>=1?"scale(1)":"scale(0.2)",transition:"all .55s cubic-bezier(.34,1.56,.64,1)",marginBottom:30,zIndex:1}}><div style={{width:104,height:104,borderRadius:32,background:t.grad,display:"flex",alignItems:"center",justifyContent:"center",boxShadow:`0 32px 90px ${t.purple}70,0 0 0 1px ${t.purple}40`,position:"relative"}}><MessageCircle size={54} color="#fff" fill="#fff"/><div style={{position:"absolute",top:-4,right:-4,width:28,height:28,borderRadius:9,background:"linear-gradient(135deg,#f5c542,#ff8c42)",display:"flex",alignItems:"center",justifyContent:"center",boxShadow:"0 4px 12px #f5c54260"}}><Lightning size={13} color="#fff" fill="#fff"/></div></div></div><div style={{opacity:p>=2?1:0,transform:p>=2?"translateY(0)":"translateY(26px)",transition:"all .5s ease",textAlign:"center",zIndex:1}}><div style={{fontFamily:"'Sora',sans-serif",fontWeight:800,fontSize:48,letterSpacing:-2.5,background:t.grad,WebkitBackgroundClip:"text",WebkitTextFillColor:"transparent",lineHeight:1}}>ZynoChat</div><div style={{fontSize:12,color:t.textSub,marginTop:8,letterSpacing:1,textTransform:"uppercase",fontFamily:"'Sora',sans-serif"}}>Secure · Fast · Unlimited</div></div><div style={{opacity:p>=3?1:0,transform:p>=3?"translateY(0)":"translateY(18px)",transition:"all .45s ease .1s",textAlign:"center",marginTop:34,zIndex:1}}><div style={{display:"inline-flex",alignItems:"center",gap:12,background:`${t.card}dd`,border:`1px solid ${t.border}`,borderRadius:18,padding:"12px 24px",backdropFilter:"blur(12px)"}}><div style={{width:8,height:8,borderRadius:"50%",background:t.green,boxShadow:`0 0 10px ${t.green}`,animation:"pDot 1.5s ease-in-out infinite"}}/><span style={{fontFamily:"'Sora',sans-serif",fontWeight:700,color:t.text,fontSize:15}}>Welcome to ZynoChat 👋</span></div></div><div style={{position:"absolute",bottom:50,left:60,right:60,zIndex:1}}><div style={{height:2,background:t.card,borderRadius:2,overflow:"hidden"}}><div style={{height:"100%",background:t.grad,borderRadius:2,transition:"width 1.1s ease",width:`${Math.min(p*34,100)}%`}}/></div></div></div>;}

